# Job Application Tracker

A practical tool to track job applications, status, and statistics.

## ✨ Features
- Add new job applications
- Track status (Applied, Interview, Rejected, Offer)
- View all applications
- Export to CSV
- Data saved in JSON

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python 3
- JSON & CSV handling

## 🚀 How to Run
```bash
python main.py
